---
// src/pages/en/about.astro
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import {Image} from 'astro:assets';
import aboutImage from '../../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
---
<PageLayout
        title="About"
        description="Discover my journey, my artistic vision, and my passion for cinema."
>
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "Person",
        "name": "Hamza Dar",
        "url": Astro.url.href,
        "jobTitle": "Filmmaker",
        "description": "A short film director passionate about creating unique stories and capturing moments of authenticity."
    })}/>

    <style>
        .about-image {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
    </style>

    <Image src={aboutImage} alt="Portrait of the director Hamza Dar" class="about-image" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />

    <h2>My Journey</h2>
    <p>
        Ever since I was young, cinema has been my greatest passion. I started creating my own stories with a small
        camera, exploring the streets of my hometown and turning everyday life into extraordinary tales. After studying
        film, I embarked on a career as an independent director to bring my unique vision to life.
    </p>

    <h2>My Artistic Vision</h2>
    <p>
        I believe that cinema is a powerful tool for exploring the human condition. My films seek to capture moments of
        authenticity, ask profound questions, and evoke emotion. I am particularly drawn to intimate stories that reveal
        universal truths, using a refined visual aesthetic to enhance the narrative.
    </p>
    <p>
        Each project is a new adventure, an opportunity to collaborate with diverse talents and push the boundaries of
        my creativity.
    </p>
</PageLayout>
